#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn6.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn6.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 15. Parinibbānasutta → parinibbāṇasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn6.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Parinibbānasutta "
msgstr "15. Final Extinguishment "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.158, sc1
msgctxt "sn6.15:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kusinārāyaṃ viharati upavattane mallānaṃ sālavane antarena yamakasālānaṃ parinibbānasamaye. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying between a pair of sal trees in the sal forest of the Mallas at Upavattana near Kusinārā at the time of his final extinguishment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.15:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to the mendicants: "

msgctxt "sn6.15:1.3"
msgid "“handa dāni, bhikkhave, āmantayāmi vo: "
msgstr "“Come now, mendicants, I say to you all: "

msgctxt "sn6.15:1.4"
msgid "‘vayadhammā saṅkhārā, appamādena sampādethā’”ti. "
msgstr "‘Conditions fall apart. Persist with diligence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.15:1.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ tathāgatassa pacchimā vācā. "
msgstr "These were the Realized One’s last words. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ → paṭhamajjhānaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts2)
#. VAR: Paṭhamā jhānā → paṭhamajjhānā (bj, s1-3, km, pts2) | pathamajhānā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn6.15:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Paṭhamā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Dutiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Tatiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Catutthā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Ākāsānañcāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Viññāṇañcāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Ākiñcaññāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Nevasaññānāsaññāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ samāpajji. "
msgstr "Then the Buddha entered the first absorption. Emerging from that, he entered the second absorption. Emerging from that, he successively entered into and emerged from the third absorption, the fourth absorption, the dimension of infinite space, the dimension of infinite consciousness, the dimension of nothingness, and the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception. Then he entered the cessation of perception and feeling. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.341, sc3
msgctxt "sn6.15:3.1"
msgid "Saññāvedayitanirodhā vuṭṭhahitvā nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Nevasaññānāsaññāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Ākiñcaññāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Viññāṇañcāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ samāpajji. Ākāsānañcāyatanā vuṭṭhahitvā catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Catutthā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Tatiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Dutiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Paṭhamā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Dutiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Tatiyā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajji. Catutthā jhānā vuṭṭhahitvā samanantaraṃ bhagavā parinibbāyi. "
msgstr "Then he emerged from the cessation of perception and feeling and entered the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception. Emerging from that, he successively entered into and emerged from the dimension of nothingness, the dimension of infinite consciousness, the dimension of infinite space, the fourth absorption, the third absorption, the second absorption, and the first absorption. Emerging from that, he successively entered into and emerged from the second absorption and the third absorption. Then he entered the fourth absorption. Emerging from that the Buddha immediately became fully extinguished. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.15:3.2"
msgid "Parinibbute bhagavati saha parinibbānā brahmā sahampati imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "When the Buddha became fully extinguished, along with the full extinguishment, Brahmā Sahampati recited this verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.1"
msgid "“Sabbeva nikkhipissanti, "
msgstr "“All creatures in this world "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.2"
msgid "bhūtā loke samussayaṃ; "
msgstr "must lay down this bag of bones. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.3"
msgid "Yattha etādiso satthā, "
msgstr "For even a Teacher such as this, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.4"
msgid "loke appaṭipuggalo; "
msgstr "unrivaled in the world, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.5"
msgid "Tathāgato balappatto, "
msgstr "the Realized One, attained to power, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:4.6"
msgid "sambuddho parinibbuto”ti. "
msgstr "the Buddha became fully extinguished.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.342, sc5
msgctxt "sn6.15:5.1"
msgid "Parinibbute bhagavati saha parinibbānā sakko devānamindo imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "When the Buddha became fully extinguished, Sakka, lord of gods, recited this verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn6.15:6.1"
msgid "“Aniccā vata saṅkhārā, "
msgstr "“Oh! Conditions are impermanent, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:6.2"
msgid "uppādavayadhammino; "
msgstr "their nature is to rise and fall; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:6.3"
msgid "Uppajjitvā nirujjhanti, "
msgstr "having arisen, they cease; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:6.4"
msgid "tesaṃ vūpasamo sukho”ti. "
msgstr "their stilling is true bliss.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn6.15:7.1"
msgid "Parinibbute bhagavati saha parinibbānā āyasmā ānando imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "When the Buddha became fully extinguished, Venerable Ānanda recited this verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn6.15:8.1"
msgid "“Tadāsi yaṃ bhiṃsanakaṃ, "
msgstr "“Then there was terror! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:8.2"
msgid "tadāsi lomahaṃsanaṃ; "
msgstr "Then they had goosebumps! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:8.3"
msgid "Sabbākāravarūpete, "
msgstr "When the Buddha, endowed with all fine qualities, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:8.4"
msgid "sambuddhe parinibbute”ti. "
msgstr "became fully extinguished.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.159, sc9
msgctxt "sn6.15:9.1"
msgid "Parinibbute bhagavati saha parinibbānā āyasmā anuruddho imā gāthāyo abhāsi: "
msgstr "When the Buddha became fully extinguished, Venerable Anuruddha recited this verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "sn6.15:10.1"
msgid "“Nāhu assāsapassāso, "
msgstr "“There was no more breathing "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:10.2"
msgid "ṭhitacittassa tādino; "
msgstr "for the poised one of steady heart. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:10.3"
msgid "Anejo santimārabbha, "
msgstr "Imperturbable, committed to peace, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:10.4"
msgid "cakkhumā parinibbuto. "
msgstr "the seer became fully extinguished. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.1"
msgid "Asallīnena cittena, "
msgstr "He put up with painful feelings "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.2"
msgid "vedanaṃ ajjhavāsayi; "
msgstr "without flinching. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.3"
msgid "Pajjotasseva nibbānaṃ, "
msgstr "The liberation of his heart "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.4"
msgid "vimokkho cetaso ahū”ti. "
msgstr "was like the extinguishing of a lamp.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn6.15:11.5"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.343, sc12
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.1"
msgid "Brahmāsanaṃ devadatto, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.2"
msgid "Andhakavindo aruṇavatī; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.3"
msgid "Parinibbānena ca desitaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.4"
msgid "Idaṃ brahmapañcakanti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn6.15:12.5"
msgid "Brahmasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on Brahmā are complete."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
